{"tid":196070,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"咬人不滿對手 誰比飽飯您食","createTime":"2017-04-11T04:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T23:04:14.000Z","uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0c92e122c6f3a81dd96534c8530d292d67e5ca7","tid":196070,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"丹尼爾出自巴塞，曾在巴塞一線隊效力八年，之後轉會到了祖雲達斯。今場比賽，祖記的首粒入球便是由丹尼爾攻入的，丹尼爾在入球後沒有掩飾自己的喜悅情緒，對入球進行了慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n　　這樣的舉動顯然會讓巴塞球員感到不爽，比賽結束之後，蘇亞雷斯找到丹尼爾，在他耳邊說了些什麼。根據西班牙電視台節目El Chiringuito的說法，蘇亞雷斯當時說的是：<span style=\"color: red;\">「別忘了當初是誰給你飯吃的。」</span><br />\n<br />\n　　報導稱，丹尼爾也給出了回應，他對蘇亞雷斯說：「現在養我的是祖記。」<br />\n<br />\n　　賽後接受採訪時，丹尼爾表示：「如果我能在球場上有什麼成就，都要感謝祖記。巴塞？不了。」"},{"pid":"717630ae18c8f35b49cb5a932255c301950ef95c","tid":196070,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T05:01:32.000Z","msg":"丹狗入撚到波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2e043191ceca2b2c7ded5a74d274f1e85c58c4","tid":196070,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99564ba3ea6e4bf55ec3e647404b394f9b3980e4","tid":196070,"uid":62981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:59:17.000Z","msg":"巴塞?不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77367004d90fce6d6f9fffdd5199ffe0ca0e944e","tid":196070,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T23:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴塞?不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD翻改到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 